In March of <link xlink:type="simple" xlink:href="../660/38660.xml">
1672</link>, Charles II issued a <product wordnetid="104007894" confidence="0.8">
<law wordnetid="108441203" confidence="0.8">
<creation wordnetid="103129123" confidence="0.8">
<artifact wordnetid="100021939" confidence="0.8">
